As the FIRST house to ever grace the legendary stage on season 1 of @legendarymax, myself and The Gorgeous House Of Gucci are deeply saddened that the legendary road ends here, after only 3 beautiful seasons!However, I am beyond grateful to have had the experience to show the entire world the greatness and creativity that the wonderful world of ballroom has to offer!! 

With so much fear, excitement and love in our hearts, we were eager to perform and show the world what it has been missing all these decades!! Blood, sweat, and tears went into each and every performance and trophy or not it was truly worth it! 

This opportunity has opened many doors for many of its contenders and we will forever continue to grown in that light! 

Thanks @legendarymax and @scout.productions for your dedication in sharing our world and talents on a global level!! 

To the judge’s, @luxurylaw @jameelajamil @theestallion  and Leyomi, thanks for your constructive criticism and feedback. The Shade, the love and the reads all helped us strengthen our crafts, minds and our confidence!! You are all amazing and we thank you!!

Gucci Fans!! You are the real MVP’s!!! I felt your love all around the world!! 🫶🏽😘🫶🏽💖

I am forever humbled and blessed to have had this opportunity. And from it, I have much more to develop and share!! 
Forever, your legendary Father Gucci!!

🌹❤️‍🔥❤️ GOOD MORNING ❤️❤️‍🔥🌹 

Next Thursday, February 9th, I Will be hosting an Interactive Social Speed Dating Event where Gay Dating potentials will come together, Get familiar with new faces and hopefully Leave with a great feeling about Love for the future!! 
This will be a great chance to connect with others while also discussing topics surrounding healthy sexual literacy, PrEP and becoming comfortable with having those important bedroom conversations that are often skipped over in the heat of the moment. 

This event will be held at @broadwaynightclub in Norfolk from 7-10pm. There is no dress code, but You definitely want to come looking and feeling your best and ready to mingle! 

Light refreshments will be available at our Sweet bar 🧁 🍬 along with Bartenders to whip up some of your favorite cocktails 🍹🍸 while you enjoy music and the company of new faces!! 

PrEP services and Complementary/ Confidential HIV Testing will be available. 

Please share and invite those who you know will be interested. 

COUPLES ARE INVITED TOO!! 👨🏽‍❤️‍👨🏽

Can’t wait to see you there!! 

With love, Jarrell and @lgbtlifecenter

I truly want to thank each and every person that came out to the Valentine’s Date PrEP Speed Dating event I threw Last night on be half of the @lgbtlifecenter!! The night was SOOO AWESOME! All the guys had such a great time and I got really really good feedback from my organization and from the community! It’s important that we support one another, spread love and Date healthily! 
I also want to thank all the contributors who lent me a hand in setting up and organizing. Team work truly makes the dream work!! 

This was just the first of many dope events that I plan to organize for the community! 

These are a few shots and videos of the event and some of the guys that came out. 

THANKS FOR THE SUPPORT 🌹😍❤️‍🔥🥰💐
